    dc:title "A new species of the genus Stigmatonotum (Hemiptera: Heteroptera: Rhyparochromidae) from Japan, with notes on related species from the East Palaearctic and Oriental Regions" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10134077>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10134079>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10134081>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10134083>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10134085> ;
